verbose_text: In addition, siRNA-ANXA1 upregulated the levels of B-cell lymphoma-2 (Bcl-2) and pro-caspase-3, and downregulated the levels of Bcl-2-associated X protein, cleaved-caspase-3, TNF-alpha, IL-1beta, IL-6 and IL-8.
evidence: levels of Bcl-2-associated X protein, cleaved-caspase-3, TNF-alpha, IL-1beta, IL-6
